article_title: Hamas intends to keep its new leader's identity confidential.
sentence: The  official  added  that  Hamas  had  been  surprised  by  the  way  Yahya  Sinwar  had  been  killed  last  week  as  their  understanding  had  been  that  he  was  in  a  much  more  secure  location  at  the  time  of  his  assassination.
